Subject: Clients are not connecting to the server
Description:
Hello, I received this from the customer.
I'm running into issues provisioning the client through Intune, its installing successfully but the clients don't actually have a connection to the server. So at the moment I have a few clients installed on endpoints, they aren't talking or receiving policy! Hopefully somebody can help me figure out an easy way to get it corrected.
Solution_Comment__c: used the zap tool on the computers that were problematic and the agent installed successfully.
